{"title":"木棍分割","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":250,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-1870","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p><span>有n根木棍, 第i根木棍的长度为Li,n根木棍依次连结了一起, 总共有n-1个连接处. 现在允许你最多砍断m个连接处, 砍完后n根木棍被分成了很多段,要求满足总长度最大的一段长度最小, 并且输出有多少种砍的方法使得总长度最大的一段长度最小. 并将结果</span><span>&lt;a href=\"http://61.187.179.132/JudgeOnline/discuss/thread.php?tid=380\"&gt;mod 10007。。。&lt;/a&gt;</span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p><span>输入文件第一行有2个数n,m. 接下来n行每行一个正整数Li,表示第i根木棍的长度.</span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p><span>输出有2个数, 第一个数是总长度最大的一段的长度最小值, 第二个数是有多少种砍的方法使得满足条件.</span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p><span>3 2 </span><br><span> 1 </span><br><span> 1</span><br><span> 10</span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p><span>10 2</span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p><span>两种砍的方法: (1)(1)(10)和(1 1)(10)</span><br><span> 数据范围 </span><br><span> n&lt;=50000, 0&lt;=m&lt;=min(n-1,1000).</span><br><span> 1&lt;=Li&lt;=1000.</span></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}